          <h3 class="fs-3 fw-bold text-primary">Why Fun Asia Tour</h3>
          <p class="fs-3">Knowing that many Asian countries are emerging tourism markets and many local attractions are still little known to the outside world, we design itineraries by combining world-famous sites with hidden attractions that others do not know yet.</p>
          <p class="fs-3">Knowing that the time of fixed itineraries, fixed days and size tour groups is over, we organise your tour in a way that gives you the freedom to decide your own itineraries, to choose the time and number of days on tour suitable to your personal plan, time schedule and interests.</p>
          <p class="fs-3">And all is with the price that is daily, year-round fixed, surely competitive and transparent.</p>
        </div>
