          <h3 class="fs-3 fw-bold text-primary">Expert Tour Organisers and Travel Management Executives</h3>
          <p class="fs-3">We at Fun Asia Tour are a team of experienced tour organisers, airline management executives and travel consultants who know well these underserved tourism markets of Asia and what more Asian countries can offer the world. We do not only create chances for you to see and hear but to deeply experience. In other words, we will take you much closer to the country and the people, indulge you with the unspoiled nature, their culture, history and the colourful daily life.</p>
          <p class="fs-3">We now begin with Malaysia, Thailand and Vietnam - the 3 widely chosen holiday destinations by the world and gradually expand to the whole of Asia.</p>
        </div>
